name: ARBForHFrEF
title: ARB for HFrEF
purpose: (Clinical Focus: ARBs which have HFrEF as approved indication, per Clinical Pharmacology (https://www.clinicalkey.com/pharmacology/resources/overviews?id=1216675#TherapeuticUse)),(Data Element Scope: RxCUIs fitting exclusion and inclusion criteria.),(Inclusion Criteria: Medications containing candesartan, losartan, and valsartan, including combination medications.),(Exclusion Criteria: Non-prescribable medications, and medications containing azilsartan, irbesartan, olmesartan, and telmisartan.)
